sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_client_script"><sys_ux_client_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><includes/><macroponent display_value="Landing Page">7ca98230f900f010cf4c983ee51e3079</macroponent><name>Refresh landing</name><required_translations>[ ]</required_translations><script><![CDATA[/**
 * @param {params} params
 * @param {api} params.api
 * @param {any} params.event
 * @param {any} params.imports
 */
function handler({api, event, helpers, imports}) {
    if(event.payload.name !== 'refresh'){
        return;
    }
    api.data.evam_mytasks.refresh();
    api.data.evam_myrequests.refresh();

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_client_script"><sys_ux_client_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><includes/><macroponent display_value="Order success">f0a982304600f010aa89b2a52603f56b</macroponent><name>View request redirection</name><required_translations>[ ]</required_translations><script><![CDATA[/**
 * @param {params} params
 * @param {api} params.api
 * @param {any} params.event
 * @param {any} params.imports
 */
function handler({
    api,
    event,
    helpers,
    imports
}) {
    let {
        table,
        sysId
    } = api.context.props;

    const route = "record_request";

    if (table != "sc_request") {
        table = table == "incident" ? "incident" : "task";
        api.emit('NAV_ITEM_SELECTED', {
            route,
            fields: {
                table,
                sysId
            }
        });
    } else {
        api.emit('NAV_ITEM_SELECTED', {
            route,
            fields: {
                table : "sc_req_item",
                sysId : api.data.request_item_data_broker_1.output.sysId
            }
        });
    }
}]]></script><script_api_version>2.0.0</script_api_version><sys_class_name>sys_ux_client_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:47</sys_created_on><sys_id>fca982308900f0105f49a03616e7ca6b</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>View request redirection</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_client_script_fca982308900f0105f49a03616e7ca6b</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:47</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_client_script></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_data_broker_transform"><sys_ux_data_broker_transform action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><acl_failure_result/><api_name>x_snc_ehw.Display value block transform</api_name><description>This is used to transform the server fetched data into label value pairs to be displayed by the 'display value block' component</description><mutates_server_data>false</mutates_server_data><name>Display value block transform</name><output_schema/><private>false</private><props>[
  {
    "name": "catBroker",
    "label": "catalog item broker",
    "fieldType": "json",
    "valueType": "object",
    "readOnly": false,
    "mandatory": true,
    "description": "Graphql Query Output"
  },
 {
    "name": "table",
    "label": "Table",
    "fieldType": "json",
    "valueType": "object",
    "readOnly": false,
    "mandatory": true,
    "description": "Graphql Query Output"
  },
 {
    "name": "user",
    "label": "Logged in user",
    "fieldType": "json",
    "valueType": "object",
    "readOnly": false,
    "mandatory": true,
    "description": "Graphql Query Output"
  },
 {
    "name": "requested",
    "label": "Requested For",
    "fieldType": "json",
    "valueType": "object",
    "readOnly": false,
    "mandatory": true,
    "description": "Graphql Query Output"
  }
]</props><required_translations>[{"message":"Table","comment":""},{"message":"Requested For","comment":""},{"message":"Logged in user","comment":""},{"message":"Graphql Query Output","comment":""},{"message":"catalog item broker","comment":""}]</required_translations><schema_version>1.0.0</schema_version><script><![CDATA[function transform(input) {
    var modelArray = [];
    var modelData = input.catBroker;
    var table = input.table;
    var user = input.user;
    var requestedFor = input.requested;
    function block(label, type, value) {
        var out = {};
		var labelNew = gs.getMessage("{0}", label);
		out.label = labelNew;
		var outval = {};
		outval.type = type;
		outval.value = value;
		out.value = outval;
		return out;
	}
    function getDate(item) {
        if (item != undefined && item.displayValue != "" && item.displayValue != null) {
            var itemDate = new GlideDate();
            itemDate.setValue(item.displayValue);
			item.displayValue = itemDate.getValue();
            return item;
        }
    }
    function addToModel(item, label) {
        if (item != undefined && item.displayValue != "" && item.displayValue != null) {
            modelArray.push(block(label, "string", item.displayValue));
        }
    }
    if (table === 'sc_req_item') {
        addToModel(modelData.state, "State");
        addToModel(modelData.stage, "Stage");
        addToModel(getDate(modelData.due_date), "Due date");
        if (requestedFor != undefined && requestedFor != null && requestedFor != user) {
            modelArray.push(block("Requested for", "string", requestedFor));
        }
        addToModel(modelData.number, "Request number");
        addToModel(modelData.quantity, "Quantity");
        addToModel(modelData.price, "Price");
        var recurringPrice = modelData.recurring_price || {};
        if (recurringPrice.displayValue && recurringPrice.displayValue.substring(1) !== "0.00") {
            modelArray.push(block("Recurring price", "string", recurringPrice.displayValue));
        }
        addToModel(modelData.recurring_frequency, "Recurring frequency");
    } else if (table === 'incident') {
        addToModel(modelData.state, "State");
        addToModel(getDate(modelData.due_date), "Due date");
        addToModel(modelData.number, "Request number");
        addToModel(modelData.caller_id, "Caller");
        addToModel(modelData.urgency, "Urgency");
        addToModel(modelData.cmdb_ci, "Configuration item");
        addToModel(modelData.assigned_to, "Assigned to");
    } else {
        addToModel(modelData.state, "State");
        addToModel(getDate(modelData.due_date), "Due date");
        addToModel(modelData.number, "Request number");
    }

	addToModel(getDate(modelData.sys_created_on), "Creation date");
    addToModel(getDate(modelData.sys_updated_on), "Last update");
    return modelArray;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:44</sys_created_on><sys_id>7ca98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Display value block transform</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform_7ca98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:44</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_data_broker_transform><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=7ca98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e"/></record_update>

	}catch(e){}
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:46</sys_created_on><sys_id>30a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193f</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Get approver sysId</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform_30a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193f</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:46</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_data_broker_transform><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=30a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193f"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_ux_data_broker_transform_b8a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_data_broker_transform"><sys_ux_data_broker_transform action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><acl_failure_result/><api_name>x_snc_ehw.Data row evam broker - My Tasks</api_name><description>Used to transform EVAM data to fit design of custom portal data row cards.</description><mutates_server_data>false</mutates_server_data><name>Data row evam broker - My Tasks</name><output_schema/><private>false</private><props>[
  {
    "name": "evambroker",
    "label": "EVAM Broker",
    "fieldType": "json",
    "valueType": "object",
    "readOnly": false,
    "mandatory": true,
    "description": "Graphql Query Output"
  }
]
</props><required_translations>[{"message":"EVAM Broker","comment":""},{"message":"Graphql Query Output","comment":""}]</required_translations><schema_version>1.0.0</schema_version><script><![CDATA[function transform(input) {
	for(var i = 0; i < input.evambroker.items.length; i++){
		var model = input.evambroker.items[i].propValues;
		var currDate = new GlideDate();
		var dueDate = new GlideDate();
		dueDate.setValue(model.model.due_date);
		if(model.model.due_date != ""){
				model.highlightedHeaderLabel = gs.getMessage("Approval due: {0}", dueDate);
				if(currDate.getDisplayValue() > dueDate.getDisplayValue()){
					model.highlightedHeaderBkgColor = "critical";
					model.highlightedHeaderLabel = gs.getMessage("Approval overdue: {0}", dueDate);
				}
		}
		model.title = gs.getMessage("Approval Request: {0}", model.title);
		if(model.model.table == "sc_req_item"){
			if(model.model.recurring_frequency != null){
				model.subtitle = model.subtitle + " + " + model.model.recurring_price + " " + model.model.recurring_frequency;
			}
		}
    if(model.model.sys_created_on != null){
			var createdDate = new GlideDate();
			createdDate.setValue(model.model.sys_created_on);
			model.detailValueOne = createdDate.toString();
		}
	}
	return input;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:45</sys_created_on><sys_id>b8a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Data row evam broker - My Tasks</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform_b8a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:45</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_data_broker_transform><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=b8a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_client_script"><sys_ux_client_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><includes/><macroponent display_value="Article page">f4a982301500f0106fa01e39be54126a</macroponent><name>Toggle Comment Reaction</name><required_translations>[ ]</required_translations><script><![CDATA[function handler({ api, event, imports }) {
  var likeCommentPayload = {
    operation: {
      dataElementId: "like_knowledge_comment",
      operationName: "EXECUTE"
    },
    operationPayload: {
      commentId: event.payload.commentId,
      articleId: api.context.props.sysId
    }
  }

  var unlikeCommentPayload = {
    operation: {
      dataElementId: "unlike_knowledge_comment",
      operationName: "EXECUTE"
    },
    operationPayload: {
      commentId: event.payload.commentId,
      articleId: api.context.props.sysId
    }
  }

  if (event.payload.reaction) {
    api.emit("UXF_DB_OP_TRIGGER_REQUESTED", likeCommentPayload);
  } else {
    api.emit("UXF_DB_OP_TRIGGER_REQUESTED", unlikeCommentPayload);
  }
}
]]></script><script_api_version>1.0.0</script_api_version><sys_class_name>sys_ux_client_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:46</sys_created_on><sys_id>78a982305f00f010b780f22a5f857b6c</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Toggle Comment Reaction</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_client_script_78a982305f00f010b780f22a5f857b6c</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:46</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_client_script></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_client_script"><sys_ux_client_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><includes/><macroponent display_value="Landing Page">7ca98230f900f010cf4c983ee51e3079</macroponent><name>My task page redirection</name><required_translations>[ ]</required_translations><script><![CDATA[/**
 * @param {params} params
 * @param {api} params.api
 * @param {any} params.event
 * @param {any} params.imports
 */
function handler({
    api,
    event,
    helpers,
    imports
}) {
    const {
        state,
        emit,
        data
    } = api;
    let sysId = "";
    let table = "";
    try {
        sysId = data.look_up_record_3.result.sysapproval.value;
        let tableDisplayValue = data.look_up_record_3.result.sysapproval.displayValue;
        let tableStartsWith = tableDisplayValue.substring(0, 3);

        if (tableStartsWith == "INC") {
            table = "incident";
        }else if (tableStartsWith == "RIT") {
            table = "sc_req_item";
        } else {
            table = "task";
        }

        if (state.taskcard && sysId) {
            api.setState("taskcard", "");
            emit('NAV_ITEM_SELECTED', {
                route: "rec_task",
                fields: {
                    table,
                    sysId,
                    approvalId: api.state.taskcard
                }
            });
        }
    } catch (e) {}
}]]></script><script_api_version>2.0.0</script_api_version><sys_class_name>sys_ux_client_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:46</sys_created_on><sys_id>70a982304c00f0100ed8c760883dfc6b</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>My task page redirection</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_client_script_70a982304c00f0100ed8c760883dfc6b</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:46</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_client_script></record_update>

	const props = api.context.props;
	const fields = {
		searchContextConfigId: props.searchContextConfigId,
		searchTerm: props.searchTerm
	};
	const token = event.payload.paginationToken;
	const params = {
		searchFilters: props.searchFilters,
		facetFilters: props.facetFilters,
		disableSpellCheck: props.disableSpellCheck,
		paginationToken: token
	};
	global.window.scrollTo(0, 0);
	helpers.navigate.to('search', fields, params);
}]]></script><script_api_version>1.0.0</script_api_version><sys_class_name>sys_ux_client_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:49</sys_created_on><sys_id>b8a982306100f0104d6e4fc36995676a</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>handle_pagination</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_client_script_b8a982306100f0104d6e4fc36995676a</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:49</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_client_script></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_data_broker_transform"><sys_ux_data_broker_transform action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><acl_failure_result/><api_name>x_snc_ehw.Content set - Related items list</api_name><description>Used to convert the evam data to required content set format in the related items section of the catalog page of custom portal</description><mutates_server_data>false</mutates_server_data><name>Content set - Related items list</name><output_schema/><private>false</private><props>[
  {
    "name": "evambroker",
    "label": "broker",
    "fieldType": "json",
    "valueType": "object",
    "readOnly": false,
    "mandatory": true,
    "description": "Graphql Query Output"
  }
]</props><required_translations/><schema_version>1.0.0</schema_version><script><![CDATA[function transform(input) {
	for(var i = 0; i < input.evambroker.items.length; i++){
		var model = input.evambroker.items[i].propValues;
		if(model.model["related_sc_cat_item.recurring_frequency"] != null)
			model.subtitle = model.subtitle + " with " + model.model["related_sc_cat_item.recurring_price"] + " " + model.model["related_sc_cat_item.recurring_frequency"];
	}
	return input;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:45</sys_created_on><sys_id>f8a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Content set - Related items list</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform_f8a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:45</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_data_broker_transform><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=f8a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_client_script"><sys_ux_client_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><includes/><macroponent display_value="Search Page">f8a982302a00f010d3b6a1f57b059e6a</macroponent><name>Search result clicked</name><required_translations>[ ]</required_translations><script><![CDATA[function handler({
    api,
    event,
    imports
}) {
    const ACTION_NAME = event.payload.action.actionDispatch;
    var route = 'landing';
    if (ACTION_NAME == 'NAVIGATION_CATALOG_KB_ARTICLE' || ACTION_NAME == 'GENIUS_NAVIGATION_CATALOG_KB_ARTICLE') {
        route = "article";
        const fields = {
            "sysId": event.payload.action.actionPayload.sysId
        };
        api.emit('NAV_ITEM_SELECTED', {
            route,
            fields
        });
    } else if (ACTION_NAME == 'NAVIGATION' && event.payload.action.actionPayload.url !== "") {
        api.emit('NAV_ITEM_SELECTED', {
            external: {
                "url": event.payload.action.actionPayload.url
            }
        });
    } else if (ACTION_NAME == 'NAVIGATION') {
        var table = event.payload.action.actionPayload.table;
        if (table == "kb_knowledge") {
            route = "article";
        } else if (table == "sc_cat_item" && event.payload.action.actionPayload.url == "") {
            route = "catalog";
        }
        const fields = {
            "sysId": event.payload.action.actionPayload.sysId
        };
        api.emit('NAV_ITEM_SELECTED', {
            route,
            fields
        });
    } else if (ACTION_NAME == 'GENIUS_NAVIGATION_CATALOG_EXTERNAL') {
        api.emit('NAV_ITEM_SELECTED', {
            external: {
                "url": event.payload.action.actionPayload.url
            }
        });
    } else return;
}]]></script><script_api_version>2.0.0</script_api_version><sys_class_name>sys_ux_client_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:47</sys_created_on><sys_id>38a982306800f01062bf8c7e41f05c6c</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Search result clicked</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_client_script_38a982306800f01062bf8c7e41f05c6c</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:47</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_client_script></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_client_script"><sys_ux_client_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><includes/><macroponent display_value="Article page">f4a982301500f0106fa01e39be54126a</macroponent><name>Update comments</name><required_translations>[ {
  "message" : "Comment deleted.",
  "comment" : ""
}, {
  "message" : "Comment posted.",
  "comment" : ""
}, {
  "message" : "You have reached the daily limit for feedback posted by a user.",
  "comment" : ""
} ]</required_translations><script><![CDATA[/**
 * @param {params} params
 * @param {api} params.api
 * @param {any} params.event
 * @param {any} params.imports
 */
function handler({
    api,
    event,
    helpers,
    imports
}) {
    let done = false;
    let itemPath = [];

    const getPath = (items, pid, level) => {
        for (let i = 0; i < items.length; i++) {
            if (!done) {
                itemPath.length = level;

                if (items[i].id == pid) {
                    itemPath.push(i);
                    done = true;
                    return;
                } else {
                    if (items[i].children && items[i].children.length > 0) {
                        itemPath.push(i);
                        getPath(items[i].children, pid, level + 1);
                    }
                }
            } else return;
        }
    };

    const getStringPath = (path, key) => {
        let actualPath = "";

        for (let i = 0; i < path.length - 1; i++) {
            actualPath += `[${path[i]}].children`;
        }

        if (path.length != 0 && key)
            actualPath += `[${path[path.length - 1]}].${key}`;
        else if (path.length != 0)
            actualPath += `[${path[path.length - 1]}]`;

        return actualPath;
    };

    /**
     * Alternative method to lodash _.get()
     */
    const get = (obj, path) => {
        if (!path)
            return undefined;

        const pathArray = Array.isArray(path) ? path : path.match(/([^[.\]])+/g);

        return (
            pathArray.reduce((prevObj, key) => prevObj && prevObj[key], obj)
        );
    };

    /**
     * Alternative method to lodash _.set()
     */
    const set = (obj, path, value) => {
        const pathArray = Array.isArray(path) ? path : path.match(/([^[.\]])+/g);

        pathArray.reduce((acc, key, i) => {
            if (acc[key] === undefined) acc[key] = {};
            if (i === pathArray.length - 1) acc[key] = value;
            return acc[key];
        }, obj);
    };

    /**
     * Alternative method to lodash _.unset()
     */
    const unset = (obj, path) => {
        const pathArray = Array.isArray(path) ? path : path.match(/([^[.\]])+/g);

        pathArray.reduce((acc, key, i) => {
            if (i === pathArray.length - 1) {
                acc.splice(key, 1);
            }
            return acc[key];
        }, obj);
    };

    const put = function(obj, path, val) {
        var stringToPath = function(path) {
            if (typeof path !== 'string')
                return path;

            var output = [];

            path.split('.').forEach(function(item, index) {
                item.split(/\[([^}]+)\]/g).forEach(function(key) {
                    if (key.length > 0) {
                        output.push(key);
                    }
                });
            });

            return output;
        };

        path = stringToPath(path);

        var length = path.length;
        var current = obj;

        path.forEach(function(key, index) {
            if (index === length - 1) {
                current[key].unshift(val);
            } else {
                if (!current[key]) {
                    current[key] = {};
                }

                current = current[key];
            }
        });
    };

    if (event.elementId == 'get_article_details_1' && event.name == 'DATA_FETCH_SUCCEEDED') {
        if (api.data.get_article_details_1.articleDetails.showFeedbackComments) {
            api.setState('articleId', api.context.props.sysId);
        }
    } else if (event.elementId == 'retrieve_knowledge_comments' && event.name == 'DATA_FETCH_SUCCEEDED') {
        let comments = api.data.retrieve_knowledge_comments.knowledgeComments;

        if (comments) {
            api.setState('comments', comments);
        }
    } else if (event.elementId == 'insert_knowledge_comment' && event.name == 'DATA_OP_SUCCEEDED') {
        let data = JSON.parse(event.payload.data.output.data.AppKnowledge_Mutation.addComment);

        if (data.sys_id) {
            helpers.translate('Comment posted.').then((value) => {
                api.emit("NOW_UXF_PAGE#ADD_NOTIFICATIONS", {
                    items: [{
                        id: "submitCommentAlert",
                        status: "info",
                        icon: "info-circle-outline",
                        content: value,
                        action: {
                            type: "dismiss"
                        }
                    }],
                });
            });

            let comment = {
                'id': data.sys_id,
                'parent': data.parent,
                'children': data.children,
                'created': data.created_on,
                'text': data.comment_text,
                'user': {
                    'name': data.user.name,
                    'id': data.user.sys_id,
                    'avatar': data.user.avatar
                },
                'reactionCount': 0,
                'isReacted': false
            };

            let comments = api.state.comments;

            if (comment.parent) {
                getPath(comments, comment.parent, 0);

                if (done && itemPath.length > 0) {
                    api.setState('comments', []);

                    put(comments, getStringPath(itemPath, 'children'), comment);

                    api.setState('comments', comments);
                    done = false;
                    itemPath = [];
                }
            } else {
                api.setState('comments', []);
                comments.unshift(comment);
                api.setState('comments', comments);
            }
        } else {
            helpers.translate('You have reached the daily limit for feedback posted by a user.').then((value) => {
                api.emit("NOW_UXF_PAGE#ADD_NOTIFICATIONS", {
                    items: [{
                        id: "commentLimitAlert",
                        status: "critical",
                        icon: "info-circle-outline",
                        content: value,
                        action: {
                            type: "dismiss"
                        }
                    }],
                });
            });
        }
    } else if (event.elementId == 'delete_knowledge_comment' && event.name == 'DATA_OP_SUCCEEDED') {
        let comments = api.state.comments;
        let currentCommentId = api.state.currentCommentId;

        if (currentCommentId != null) {
            getPath(comments, currentCommentId, 0);
            
            if (done && itemPath.length > 0) {
                api.setState('comments', []);
                let index = itemPath[0];

                if (itemPath.length <= 1) {
                    comments.splice(index, 1);
                } else {
                    unset(comments, getStringPath(itemPath, null));
                }

                api.setState('comments', comments);
                done = false;
                itemPath = [];
            }

            helpers.translate('Comment deleted.').then((value) => {
                api.emit("NOW_UXF_PAGE#ADD_NOTIFICATIONS", {
                    items: [{
                        id: "deleteCommentAlert",
                        status: "info",
                        icon: "info-circle-outline",
                        content: value,
                        action: {
                            type: "dismiss"
                        }
                    }],
                });
            });
        }
    } else if (event.elementId == 'like_knowledge_comment' && event.name == 'DATA_OP_SUCCEEDED') {
        let comments = api.state.comments;
        let currentCommentId = api.state.currentCommentId;

        if (currentCommentId != null) {
            getPath(comments, currentCommentId, 0);

            if (done && itemPath.length > 0) {
                api.setState('comments', []);
                let path = getStringPath(itemPath, "");
                let reactionCount = get(comments, `${path}.reactionCount`);

                set(comments, `${path}.reactionCount`, reactionCount + 1);
                set(comments, `${path}.isReacted`, true);

                api.setState('comments', comments);
                done = false;
                itemPath = [];
            }
        }
    } else if (event.elementId == 'unlike_knowledge_comment' && event.name == 'DATA_OP_SUCCEEDED') {
        let comments = api.state.comments;
        let currentCommentId = api.state.currentCommentId;

        if (currentCommentId != null) {
            getPath(comments, currentCommentId, 0);

            if (done && itemPath.length > 0) {
                api.setState('comments', []);
                let path = getStringPath(itemPath, "");
                let reactionCount = get(comments, `${path}.reactionCount`);

                set(comments, `${path}.reactionCount`, reactionCount - 1);
                set(comments, `${path}.isReacted`, false);

                api.setState('comments', comments);
                done = false;
                itemPath = [];
            }
        }
    }
}]]></script><script_api_version>2.0.0</script_api_version><sys_class_name>sys_ux_client_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:47</sys_created_on><sys_id>b0a98230c800f01039dda913a556c96c</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Update comments</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_client_script_b0a98230c800f01039dda913a556c96c</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:47</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_client_script></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_data_broker_transform"><sys_ux_data_broker_transform action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><acl_failure_result/><api_name>x_snc_ehw.Catalog item variables transform</api_name><description>Used to convert the catalog item variables in label/value pairs</description><mutates_server_data>false</mutates_server_data><name>Catalog item variables transform</name><output_schema/><private>false</private><props>[
  {
    "name": "catBroker",
    "label": "catalog item broker",
    "fieldType": "json",
    "valueType": "object",
    "readOnly": false,
    "mandatory": true,
    "description": "Graphql Query Output"
  },
 {
        "name": "sysId",
        "label": "Catalog Sys Id",
        "description": "Pass the sys_id of catalog to pull related variables for",
        "readOnly": false,
        "fieldType": "string",

]</props><required_translations>[{"message":"Pass the sys_id of catalog to pull related variables for","comment":""},{"message":"Catalog Sys Id","comment":""},{"message":"Graphql Query Output","comment":""},{"message":"catalog item broker","comment":""}]</required_translations><schema_version>1.0.0</schema_version><script><![CDATA[function transform(input) {
	var modelArray = [];
    var modelData = input.catBroker.data.GlideRecord_Query.sc_req_item;
	function block(label,type,value){
		var out = {};
		out.label = label;
		var outval = {};
		outval.type = type;
		outval.value = value;
		out.value = outval;
		return out;
	}

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_data_broker_transform"><sys_ux_data_broker_transform action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><acl_failure_result/><api_name>x_snc_ehw.Transform metadata to add catalog filter</api_name><description>This is an interim way to add dynamic catalog filter before Related catalogs EVAM usecase </description><mutates_server_data>false</mutates_server_data><name>Transform metadata to add catalog filter</name><output_schema/><private>false</private><props>[
    {
        "name": "graphqlData",
        "label": "GraphQL Metadata Response",
        "description": "",
        "readOnly": false,
        "fieldType": "object",
        "mandatory": true,
        "defaultValue": ""
    },
    {
        "name": "catalogSysId",
        "label": "Catalog Sys Id",
        "description": "Pass the sys_id of catalog to pull related catalogs for",
        "readOnly": false,
        "fieldType": "string",
        "mandatory": true,
        "defaultValue": ""
    }
]</props><required_translations/><schema_version>1.0.0</schema_version><script><![CDATA[function transform(input) {

	var compositeMetadata = input
		.graphqlData
		.data
		.GlideCompositeDataMetadata_Query
		.getMetadata;
	var END_QUERY = '^EQ';
	var AND = '^';
	compositeMetadata.datasources.map(function(source) {
		if (source.table === 'sc_2_sc') {
			var catalogFilter = 'sc_cat_item=' + input.catalogSysId + END_QUERY;
			source.query = source.query? new String(source.query).replace(END_QUERY, "") + AND + catalogFilter : catalogFilter;
		}
	});
	
	return compositeMetadata;

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_data_broker_composite"><sys_ux_data_broker_composite action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><api_name>x_snc_ehw.EVAM data API with catalogId parameter binding</api_name><data_drivers>{

    },
    "elementId" : "compositeQueryMeta",
    "inputValues" : {
      "evamDefinitionId" : {
        "type": "BROKER_INTERNAL_INPUT_BINDING",
        "binding": {
          "address": [
            "evamDefinitionId"

  },
  "compositeMetaWithCatalogParameterBinding": {
    "definition" : {

        "graphqlData" : {
          "type": "BROKER_INTERNAL_STATE_BINDING",

            "address": [

              "output"
            ]
          }
        },
        "catalogSysId": {
            "type": "BROKER_INTERNAL_INPUT_BINDING",
            "binding": {
              "address": [
                "catalogSysId"
              ]
            }
        }
      },
      "elementLabel" : "Composite Data as View objects"      
  },
  "compositeDataEntities": {
    "definition" : {
      "id" : "eaafa603773300108d070d74c81061b6",

    },
    "elementId" : "compositeDataEntities",
    "inputValues" : {
      "evamMetadata" : {
        "type": "BROKER_INTERNAL_STATE_BINDING",

              "pageCursor"

  },
  "compositeDataViews": {
    "definition" : {
      "id" : "7b652701773300108d070d74c81061b8",
      "type" : "TRANSFORM"
    },
    "elementId" : "compositeDataViews",
    "inputValues" : {
      "graphqlData" : {
        "type": "BROKER_INTERNAL_STATE_BINDING",
        "binding": {
          "address": [
            "compositeDataEntities",
            "output"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    "elementLabel" : "Composite Data as View objects"
  }

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_data_broker_transform"><sys_ux_data_broker_transform action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><acl_failure_result/><api_name>x_snc_ehw.Boolean reversal transform</api_name><description>Required because the buttons prop is true to disable and false to enable, and also to fetch the Custom portal settings page text</description><mutates_server_data>false</mutates_server_data><name>Boolean reversal transform</name><output_schema/><private>false</private><props>[
  {
    "name": "broker",
    "label": "GraphQL Broker",
    "fieldType": "json",
    "valueType": "object",
    "readOnly": false,
    "mandatory": true,
    "description": "Graphql Query Output"
  }
]</props><required_translations>[{"message":"Graphql Query Output","comment":""},{"message":"GraphQL Broker","comment":""}]</required_translations><schema_version>1.0.0</schema_version><script><![CDATA[function transform(input) {
	var modelData = input.broker.data.GlideRecord_Query.sys_properties._results[0].value.value;
	var mfa = {};
	if(modelData == "false"){
		mfa.value = "true";
		mfa.text = gs.getMessage("Please enable Multi-factor authentication on the instance.");
	}
	else{
		mfa.value = "false";
		mfa.text = gs.getMessage("Configure Multi-factor authentication by clicking the button below");
	}
	return mfa;
}
]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:44</sys_created_on><sys_id>f0a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193f</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Boolean reversal transform</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform_f0a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193f</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:44</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_data_broker_transform><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=f0a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193f"/></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_client_script"><sys_ux_client_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><includes/><macroponent display_value="Landing Page">7ca98230f900f010cf4c983ee51e3079</macroponent><name>Request page redirection</name><required_translations>[ ]</required_translations><script><![CDATA[/**
 * @param {params} params
 * @param {api} params.api
 * @param {any} params.event
 * @param {any} params.imports
 */
function handler({api, event, helpers, imports}) {
     const {
        state,
        emit,
        data
    } = api;
    let sysId = "";
    const table = "task";
    try {
        sysId = data.look_up_record_2.result.task.value;
        if (state.producedRecordSysId && sysId) {
            api.setState("producedRecordSysId","");  
            emit('NAV_ITEM_SELECTED', {
                route: "record_request",
                fields: {
                    table,
                    sysId
                }
            });
        }
    } catch (e) {}
}]]></script><script_api_version>2.0.0</script_api_version><sys_class_name>sys_ux_client_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:46</sys_created_on><sys_id>38a982302800f01084447260248ac56b</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Request page redirection</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_client_script_38a982302800f01084447260248ac56b</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:46</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_client_script></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_client_script"><sys_ux_client_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><includes/><macroponent display_value="Order success">f0a982304600f010aa89b2a52603f56b</macroponent><name>Refresh submitted screen</name><required_translations>[ ]</required_translations><script><![CDATA[/**
 * @param {params} params
 * @param {api} params.api
 * @param {any} params.event
 * @param {any} params.imports
 */
function handler({
    api,
    event,
    helpers,
    imports
}) {
    let {
        table,
        sysId,
        number
    } = api.context.props;
    if(table !== "sc_request"){
        api.setState("successNumber",number);
        api.setState("successSysId",sysId);
    }else{

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_client_script"><sys_ux_client_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><includes/><macroponent display_value="Search Page">f8a982302a00f010d3b6a1f57b059e6a</macroponent><name>handle_search</name><required_translations>[ ]</required_translations><script><![CDATA[function handler({ api, event, helpers }) {
    const fields = {
        searchContextConfigId: api.context.props.searchContextConfigId
    };
    const params = {
        searchFilters: api.context.props.searchFilters
    };
    
	if (event.name === 'SN_SEARCH_RESULTS_CONTAINER#SEARCH_EXECUTED') {
		fields.searchTerm = event.payload.searchTerm;
		params.disableSpellCheck = true;
        
  	} else if (event.name === 'SN_SEARCH_COMBOBOX#SEARCH_EXECUTED') {
		fields.searchTerm = event.payload.searchTerm;
		params.disableSpellCheck = false;
        console.log("search clicked");
        api.setState('loading', true);
        api.setState('searchTerm', event.payload.searchTerm);
  	}
	//helpers.navigate.to('search', fields, params);
}]]></script><script_api_version>2.0.0</script_api_version><sys_class_name>sys_ux_client_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:45</sys_created_on><sys_id>30a982300100f010effc9c8868a3d26c</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>handle_search</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_client_script_30a982300100f010effc9c8868a3d26c</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:45</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_client_script></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_ux_data_broker_transform_74a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193f
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_data_broker_transform"><sys_ux_data_broker_transform action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><acl_failure_result/><api_name>x_snc_ehw.Data row evam broker - My Requests</api_name><description>Used to transform EVAM data to fit design of custom portal data row cards.</description><mutates_server_data>false</mutates_server_data><name>Data row evam broker - My Requests</name><output_schema/><private>false</private><props>[
  {
    "name": "evambroker",
    "label": "EVAM Broker",
    "fieldType": "json",
    "valueType": "object",
    "readOnly": false,
    "mandatory": true,
    "description": "Graphql Query Output"
  }
]
</props><required_translations>[{"message":"EVAM Broker","comment":""},{"message":"Graphql Query Output","comment":""}]</required_translations><schema_version>1.0.0</schema_version><script><![CDATA[function transform(input) {
	for(var i = 0; i < input.evambroker.items.length; i++){
		var model = input.evambroker.items[i].propValues;
		var currDate = new GlideDate();
		var dueDate = new GlideDate();
		var price = model.model.price;
		dueDate.setValue(model.model.due_date);
		if(model.model.table == "sc_req_item"){
			if(model.model.due_date != ""){
				model.highlightedHeaderLabel = gs.getMessage("Completion date: {0}", dueDate);
				if(currDate.getDisplayValue() > dueDate.getDisplayValue()){
					model.highlightedHeaderBkgColor = "critical";
				}
			}
			if(model.model.recurring_frequency != null)
				model.subtitle = model.subtitle + " + " + model.model.recurring_price + " " + model.model.recurring_frequency;
			if(price.substring(1) == "0.00" && model.model.recurring_frequency == null )
				model.subtitle = " ";
		}
		else{
			if(model.model.due_date != ""){
				model.highlightedHeaderLabel = gs.getMessage("Completion date: {0}", dueDate);
				if(currDate.getDisplayValue() > dueDate.getDisplayValue()){
					model.highlightedHeaderBkgColor = "critical";
				}
			}
		}
	}
	return input;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:48</sys_created_on><sys_id>74a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193f</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Data row evam broker - My Requests</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform_74a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193f</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:48</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_data_broker_transform><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=74a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193f"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_data_broker_transform"><sys_ux_data_broker_transform action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><acl_failure_result/><api_name>x_snc_ehw.Data row evam broker - Updated articles</api_name><description>Used to transform EVAM data to fit design of custom portal data row cards.</description><mutates_server_data>false</mutates_server_data><name>Data row evam broker - Updated articles</name><output_schema/><private>false</private><props>[
  {
    "name": "broker",
    "label": "EVAM Broker",
    "fieldType": "json",
    "valueType": "object",
    "readOnly": false,
    "mandatory": true,
    "description": "Graphql Query Output"
  }
]</props><required_translations>[{"message":"EVAM Broker","comment":""},{"message":"Graphql Query Output","comment":""}]</required_translations><schema_version>1.0.0</schema_version><script><![CDATA[function transform(input) {
	for(var i = 0; i < input.broker.items.length; i++){
		var model = input.broker.items[i].propValues;
		if(model.model.rating != ""){
			model.detailValueTwo = gs.getMessage("{0} out of 5", model.detailValueTwo);
		}
	}
	return input;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:45</sys_created_on><sys_id>34a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193f</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Data row evam broker - Updated articles</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform_34a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193f</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:45</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_data_broker_transform><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=34a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193f"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_ux_client_script_38a982301000f01023ad7fc7ba0f216a
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_client_script"><sys_ux_client_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><includes/><macroponent display_value="Landing Page">7ca98230f900f010cf4c983ee51e3079</macroponent><name>Card click redirection for My requests</name><required_translations>[ ]</required_translations><script><![CDATA[function handler({
    api,
    event,
    imports
}) {
    const {
        setState,
        emit
    } = api;

    const table = event.payload.table;
    const sysId = event.payload.sysId;
    const route = "record_request";

    if (table === "sc_req_item") {
        emit('NAV_ITEM_SELECTED', {
            route,
            fields: {
                table,
                sysId
            }
        });
    } else if(table == "incident"){
        emit('NAV_ITEM_SELECTED', {
            route,
            fields: {
                table: "incident",
                sysId
            }
        });
    }
    else{
        emit('NAV_ITEM_SELECTED', {
            route,
            fields: {
                table: "task",
                sysId
            }
        });
    }
}]]></script><script_api_version>2.0.0</script_api_version><sys_class_name>sys_ux_client_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:47</sys_created_on><sys_id>38a982301000f01023ad7fc7ba0f216a</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Card click redirection for My requests</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_client_script_38a982301000f01023ad7fc7ba0f216a</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:47</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_client_script></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_client_script"><sys_ux_client_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><includes/><macroponent display_value="Landing Page">7ca98230f900f010cf4c983ee51e3079</macroponent><name>On search </name><required_translations>[ ]</required_translations><script><![CDATA[/**
 * @param {params} params
 * @param {api} params.api
 * @param {any} params.event
 * @param {any} params.imports
 */
function handler({
    api,
    event,
    helpers,
    imports
}) {

    const {
        searchContextConfigId,
        searchTerm
    } = event.payload;
    
    api.emit('NAV_ITEM_SELECTED', {
        route: "search",
        fields: {
            searchContextConfigId,
            searchTerm
        }
    });
}]]></script><script_api_version>2.0.0</script_api_version><sys_class_name>sys_ux_client_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:46</sys_created_on><sys_id>78a98230c300f010c4bced35d89e6b6a</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>On search</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_client_script_78a98230c300f010c4bced35d89e6b6a</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:46</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_client_script></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_data_broker_transform"><sys_ux_data_broker_transform action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><acl_failure_result/><api_name>x_snc_ehw.Heading for record page</api_name><description>Heading for record page (Request) on custom portal</description><mutates_server_data>false</mutates_server_data><name>Heading for record page</name><output_schema/><private>false</private><props>[ {
    "name": "catBroker",
    "label": "lookup record broker",
    "fieldType": "json",
    "valueType": "object",
    "readOnly": false,
    "mandatory": true,
    "description": "Graphql Query Output"
  },
 {
    "name": "table",
    "label": "Table",
    "fieldType": "json",
    "valueType": "object",
    "readOnly": false,
    "mandatory": true,
    "description": "Graphql Query Output"
  }]</props><required_translations>[{"message":"Table","comment":""},{"message":"lookup record broker","comment":""},{"message":"Graphql Query Output","comment":""}]</required_translations><schema_version>1.0.0</schema_version><script><![CDATA[function transform(input){
	var table = input.table;
	var modelData = input.catBroker;
	
	var shortDescription = modelData.short_description && modelData.short_description.displayValue;
	var catalogItem = modelData.cat_item && modelData.cat_item.displayValue;
	
	if(table == "sc_req_item"){
			return {
			"title": catalogItem,
			"subtitle": shortDescription
		};
	}else{
		return {
			"title": shortDescription,
			"subtitle": catalogItem
		};
	}
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:48</sys_created_on><sys_id>34a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Heading for record page</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform_34a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:48</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_data_broker_transform><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=34a98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_client_script"><sys_ux_client_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><includes/><macroponent display_value="Article page">f4a982301500f0106fa01e39be54126a</macroponent><name>Create knowledge feedback</name><required_translations>[ ]</required_translations><script><![CDATA[function handler({
    api,
    helpers,
    event,
    imports
}) {
    const {
        context,
        data,
        state,
        setState,
        emit
    } = api;
    const {
        modal
    } = helpers;
    const insertRecord = function(table, fields, type) {
        setState("currentFeedbackAction", type);
        data.create_record_1.execute({
            table,
            templateFields: fields,
            useSetDisplayValue: ''
        });
    };
    var articleSysId = context.props.sysId;
    var templateFields = "article=" + articleSysId + "^";
    var articleData = data.get_article_details_1.articleDetails;
    var yesMessage = "Thank you for your feedback";
    var noMessage = "We'll improve the article based on your feedback.";
    const feedbackAction = state.currentFeedbackAction;

    if (event.elementId == "kb_star_rating") {
        setState('currentFeedbackAction', "rating");
        templateFields += "rating=" + event.payload.rating;
        if (articleData.enableActionableFeedbackForRating >= event.payload.rating) {
            setState('userRating', event.payload.rating);
            modal.open("[component-id$='custom_1']");
        } else {
            insertRecord('kb_feedback', templateFields, "rating");
        }
    }

    if (event.elementId == "boolean_feedback_no") {
        var showModal = (articleData.showFeedbackOptions || articleData.showFeedbackComments) && articleData.enableActionableFeedbackForHelpful;
        setState("currentFeedbackAction", "boolean_feedback");
        if (showModal) {
            setState('additionalDetails', null);
            setState("selectedReason", ["4"]);
            modal.open("[component-id$='custom_1']");
        } else {
            templateFields += "useful=no";
            setState('booleanFeedbackMessage', noMessage);
            setState('booleanFeedbackIcon', 'thumbs-down-outline');
            setState("isBooleanFeedbackButtonsHidden", true);
            insertRecord('kb_feedback', templateFields, "boolean_feedback");
        }
    } else if (event.elementId == "boolean_feedback_yes") {
        setState("currentFeedbackAction", "boolean_feedback");
        templateFields += "useful=yes";
        setState('booleanFeedbackMessage', yesMessage);
        setState('booleanFeedbackIcon', 'thumbs-up-outline');
        setState("isBooleanFeedbackButtonsHidden", true);
        insertRecord('kb_feedback', templateFields, "boolean_feedback");
        const usefulYesCount = articleData.usefulYesCount+1;
        const totalUsefulCount = articleData.totalUsefulCount+1;
        var helpPercent = (usefulYesCount && totalUsefulCount) ? 
            Math.round(usefulYesCount / totalUsefulCount *100) : 0;
        const helpPercentMessage = (helpPercent) ? helpPercent+'% found this helpful':'';
        setState('helpPercentMessage',helpPercentMessage);
        setState('isHelpPercentInfoHidden', false);
    } else if (event.elementId == "boolean_feedback_no_ignore") {

        modal.close("[component-id$='custom_1']");
        if (feedbackAction != "rating") {
            setState('booleanFeedbackMessage', noMessage);
            setState('booleanFeedbackIcon', 'thumbs-down-outline');
            setState("isBooleanFeedbackButtonsHidden", true);
            templateFields += "reason=4^useful=no";
        }
        if (feedbackAction == "rating") {
            templateFields += "reason=4^rating=" + state.userRating;
        }
        insertRecord('kb_feedback', templateFields,feedbackAction);

    } else if (event.elementId == "boolean_feedback_no_submit") {
        modal.close("[component-id$='custom_1']");
        if ((state.selectedReason)[0] != null)
            templateFields += "reason=" + (state.selectedReason)[0] + "^";
        if (state.additionalDetails != null)
            templateFields += "comments=" + state.additionalDetails + "^";
        if (feedbackAction != "rating") {
            setState('booleanFeedbackMessage', noMessage);
            setState('booleanFeedbackIcon', 'thumbs-down-outline');
            setState("isBooleanFeedbackButtonsHidden", true);
            templateFields += "useful=no";
        }
        if (feedbackAction == "rating") {
            templateFields += "rating=" + state.userRating;
        }
        insertRecord('kb_feedback', templateFields,feedbackAction);
    } else if (event.elementId == "flag_article") {
        modal.close("[component-id$='custom_2']");
        var comments = state.flagArticleContent.replaceAll("\n", "\\n").replaceAll("^", "^");
        templateFields += "flagged=true^comments=" + comments;
        setState('flagArticleContent', comments);
        if (articleData.enableActionableFeedbackForFlag)
            templateFields += "^reason=Flagged";
        insertRecord('kb_feedback', templateFields, "flag_article");
    }

    if (event.elementId == "create_record_1") {
        var items = [];
        var requestFailed = false;
		
        if (event.name == "DATA_OP_SUCCEEDED") {
            var output = event.payload.data.output.data.GlideRecord_Mutation.insert_kb_feedback;
            if (output == null) {
                requestFailed = true;
            } else {
                if (state.currentFeedbackAction == "flag_article") {
                    items.push({
                        id: "flagArticleSuccess",
                        status: "info",
                        icon: "info-circle-outline",
                        content: "Article has been flagged",
                        action: {
                            type: "dismiss"
                        }
                    });
                }
                if (state.currentFeedbackAction == "rating") {
                    items.push({
                        id: "ratingArticleSuccess",
                        status: "info",
                        icon: "info-circle-outline",
                        content: "Feedback submitted.",
                        action: {
                            type: "dismiss"
                        }
                    });
                }

                if (state.currentFeedbackAction == "boolean_feedback") {
                    items.push({
                        id: "booleanFeedbackSuccess",
                        status: "info",
                        icon: "info-circle-outline",
                        content: "Feedback submitted.",
                        action: {
                            type: "dismiss"
                        }
                    });
                }
            }
        }
        
        if (event.name == "DATA_OP_FAILED" || requestFailed) {
            items.push({
                id: "flagArticleFailure",
                status: "critical",
                icon: "info-circle-outline",
                content: "You have reached the daily limit for feedback posted by a user.",
                action: {
                    type: "dismiss"
                }
            });
        }
        if (items.length > 0) {
            emit("NOW_UXF_PAGE#ADD_NOTIFICATIONS", {
                items
            });
        }
        setState('currentFeedbackAction', "");
    }
}]]></script><script_api_version>2.0.0</script_api_version><sys_class_name>sys_ux_client_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:48</sys_created_on><sys_id>b4a982309b00f010dc919e305a32be6b</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Create knowledge feedback</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_client_script_b4a982309b00f010dc919e305a32be6b</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:48</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_client_script></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ux_data_broker_transform"><sys_ux_data_broker_transform action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><acl_failure_result/><api_name>x_snc_ehw.Request Item Data Broker</api_name><description>Data broker that returns the request itemfrom the request</description><mutates_server_data>false</mutates_server_data><name>Request Item Data Broker</name><output_schema/><private>false</private><props>[
  {
    "name": "sysId",
    "label": "Sys Id",
    "fieldType": "string",
    "valueType": "object",
    "readOnly": false,
    "mandatory": true,
    "description": "Sys Id of sc_request table"
  }
]</props><required_translations>[{"message":"Sys Id of sc_request table","comment":""},{"message":"Sys Id","comment":""}]</required_translations><schema_version>1.0.0</schema_version><script><![CDATA[function transform(input) {
    var requestSysId = input.sysId || "";
    if (requestSysId !== "") {
        var request = new GlideRecord("sc_req_item");
        request.addQuery('request', requestSysId);
        request.query();
        if (request.next()) {
            return {
				"table" : "sc_req_item",
				"sysId" : request.getUniqueValue(),
				"number" : request.getValue("number")
			};
        }
    }
    return;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>system</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-05-08 17:28:46</sys_created_on><sys_id>bca98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Request Item Data Broker</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Employee Health & Wellness" source="x_snc_ehw">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Employee Health & Wellness">b29b39b4dbccb010f4ad09c4e29619ac</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_data_broker_transform_bca98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-05-08 17:28:46</sys_updated_on></sys_ux_data_broker_transform><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=bca98230db00f010f4ad09c4e296193e"/></record_update>
